		<h2 class='diff-currentversion-title'>Revision as of 16:54, 7 December 2014</h2>
<table class="infobox vevent" style="width:22em">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="hd" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color: transparent">National Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:Pearl_harbour.png" class="image"><img alt="Pearl harbour.png" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Pearl_harbour.png/240px-Pearl_harbour.png" width="240" height="194" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Pearl_harbour.png/360px-Pearl_harbour.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Pearl_harbour.png/480px-Pearl_harbour.png 2x" data-file-width="2901" data-file-height="2351" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
